<hw>Deaf</hw> <pr>(?; 277)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To deafen.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Dryden.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

